quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,26,Soni chisimu chene mundu twan’gumbile ni lilongo lyejumu lyakulilaga (nkuligombamo) lyakuumila m’matope gakupiililila geunde
  15,27,Sano lijini twaligumbile kala kuumila ku malamba ga moto gangali lyosi
  15,28,"Soni (kumbuchilani) katema kaŵaŵechete Ambuje ŵenu kwa Achimalaika kuti: “Chisimu Une tingumbe mundu ni lilongo lyejumu lyakulilaga (nkuligombamo) lyakuumila m’matope gakupiililila geunde.”"
  15,29,"“Sano patimale kunkolosya ni kumpepelela nsimu wakuuma Kukwangu, basi munsenjelemukuchile pakunsujudila.”"
  15,30,Basi ni ŵasujudu Achimalaika wosope ŵene nakamo
  15,31,Pangaŵaga Ibulisu; jwakanile kuti aŵe pamo ni akusujudu
  15,32,"(Allah) jwatite: “E mmwe Ibulisu! Chipali chichi kukwenu chintendekasisye kuti nkaŵa pamo ni akusujudu?”"
  15,33,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Une nganimba jwanti nikunsujudila mundu jwamun’gumbile ni lilongo lyejumu lyakulilaga (nkuligombamo) lyakuumila m’matope gakupiililila geunde.”"
  15,34,"(Allah) jwatite: “Basi kopokani mwalakwemo, mwanti chisimu mmwe (sano) n’di ŵakuŵinjidwa.”"
  15,35,“Soni chisimu pachanya penu pana malweso mpaka Lisiku Lyamalipilo.”
  15,36,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Mumbanitu lipesa (lyakuti ngawa) mpaka lisiku lyatachiukulidwa (m’malembe achiiumbe wosope).”"
  15,37,"(Allah) jwatite: “Basi chisimu mmwe n’di mwa akupedwa lipesa.”"
  15,38,"“Kwikanila lisiku lya ndema jakumanyika (jagombedwa lipenga lyandanda, pele ni patinchiwila).”"
  15,39,"Jwalakwe jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Ligongo lyanti munechelele kusokonechela, basi chinasalalichisye kwene ŵanganyao pa chilambo (litala lyesokonechele), ni chinasokonesye kwene ŵanaose.”"
  15,40,“Pangaŵaga achikapolo Ŵenu ŵakuswejesyedwa mwa ŵanganyao.”
  15,41,"(Allah) jwatite: “Ali nilitala lya Kukwangu lyalili lyagoloka.”"
  15,42,"“Chisimu achikapolo Ŵangu nganinkola mmwejo pa ŵanganyao machili, ikaŵeje aŵala ŵatakankuyeje (mwakusaka kwao) mwa akusokonechela.”"
  15,43,Soni chisimu Jahannama ni malo gao gaakupedwa chilanga ŵanaose
  15,44,"Jikwete milango nsano najiŵili, nnango uliose ukwete liunjili mwa ŵanganyao lyegaŵidwegaŵidwe"